{"tid":2040283,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"★【樓市震散】買家縮沙　舖租大冧","createTime":"2020-05-28T12:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T14:39:40.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92558bdd8581fa4294cc665d717ec4695aad1be1","tid":2040283,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:59:18.000Z","msg":"【樓市震散】東涌東環買家撻訂縮沙；黃埔價位回到去年3月；尖沙咀舖月租高位瀉90%。<br />\n<br />\n後市去向未明，二手市場有買家撻訂縮沙。東涌東環兩房單位，月中以約665萬港元售出，買家睇淡看市，最終放棄交易，估計訂金連佣金損失至少逾30餘萬元。而藍籌屋苑紅磡花園花園就錄劈價出貨個案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200528/bkn-20200528203717137-0528_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200528%2Fbkn-20200528203717137-0528_00842_001.html&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu4c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=094b8a95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200528/bkn-20200528203717137-0528_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ebe41e03cdeb55a2f216378761bfe97e3dba8d6c","tid":2040283,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057411692ddbf8f60e5c8efd37da3942f0031937","tid":2040283,"uid":29093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公安先生 ,  連登唔見左啲 AA 狗呀,  可唔可以幫我搵返佢地呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cff6a25b33416c92f9eb74b36c4bb66399d369f","tid":2040283,"uid":274149,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:02:02.000Z","msg":"冧都唔買，買英國樓好過"},{"pid":"fabb43ddd8396a0c6dfb1a32c6b